	   <tr><td colspan=2>Friend gave my mage this staff recently...<br><br>First, it is not a proc, I am able to right click and get the effect as long as it is wielded. Second, it DOES take 3 Cat's Eye Agate to cast from this damn thing (Gee, thanks Verant). Third, casting time is about the same as the spell (Gee, thank Verant). Fourth, I am able to use it at 53rd level, but I already have the next upgrade to the spell (Gee, thanks Verant).<br><br> So by the time you get this staff or are able to use it you won't have a need for it and you will still need to carry about enough agate to choke a whale... what a great idea (Gee, thanks Verant).<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
